Image.Alt: A troop photo in black and white. There are names under the photo. The text reads: Earl Brist, Jack Ray, Ray Baker, Peter Andrews, Tom Latham, Bill Grotan, Al Bleadow, G Kirsh, David Van De Wal, Bob Sancomb, Irv Scott, Ray Schroeder, Bill Stolp, Rev Ton, Donald Paul, Ed Fulgo, Ed Hotaling.
Image.Caption: Troop photo from around 1935. Most of the names of the scouts have been recorded on the photo. Unfortunately, there are a couple of names missing.
